  "title": "活性炭与小苏打：终极对比",
  "excerpt": "小苏打失效了？看看为什么89%的人选择活性炭。令人震惊的测试揭示哪种对猫砂气味更有效！",
  "content": "<header class=\"mb-12\">\n            <h1 class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50\">\n              活性炭与小苏打：终极对比\n            </h1>\n            <p class=\"text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed\">\n              两种流行的除臭技术正面交锋。我们研究了科学原理、有效性以及每种方法的实际表现。\n            </p>\n          </header>\n\n          <div class=\"prose prose-lg max-w-none dark:prose-dark\">\n            <p class=\"text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200\">\n              说到控制猫砂异味，两种主要技术主导市场：活性炭和小苏打。\n              两者都有其优点，但哪一种真正能为猫主人提供更好的效果？\n            </p>\n\n            <h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50\">\n              各技术的工作原理\n            </h2>\n\n            <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 my-8\">\n              <div class=\"bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/20 p-6 rounded-lg\">\n                <h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-200\">\n                  活性炭\n                </h3>\n                <p class=\"text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300\">\n                  通过<strong>分子吸附</strong>工作。多孔结构将异味分子\n                  捕获在微观孔隙内，将它们从空气中物理去除。\n                </p>\n              </div>\n\n              <div class=\"bg-orange-50 dark:bg-orange-900/20 p-6 rounded-lg\">\n                <h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-orange-800 dark:text-orange-200\">\n                  小苏打\n                </h3>\n                <p class=\"text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300\">\n                  通过<strong>pH中和</strong>工作。碱性特性中和酸性异味\n                  化合物，降低其气味强度。\n                </p>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"mb-8\">\n              \n              <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 text-center mt-2\">\n                性能测试揭示了技术之间的显著差异\n              </p>\n            </div>\n\n            <h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50\">\n              性能对比\n            </h2>\n\n            <div class=\"overflow-x-auto\">\n              <table class=\"w-full border-collapse border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 my-8\">\n                <thead>\n                  <tr class=\"bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800\">\n                    <th class=\"border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2 text-left text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100\">因素</th>\n                    <th class=\"border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2 text-left text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-200\">活性炭</th>\n                    <th class=\"border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2 text-left text-orange-800 dark:text-orange-200\">小苏打</th>\n                  </tr>\n                </thead>\n                <tbody>\n                  <tr>\n                    <td class=\"border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2 font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100\">异味消除</td>\n                    <td class=\"border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300\">物理去除异味分子</td>\n                    <td class=\"border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300\">中和一些异味化合物</td>\n                  </tr>\n                  <tr>\n                    <td class=\"border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2 font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100\">持续时间</td>\n                    <td class=\"border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300\">4-6周有效性</td>\n                    <td class=\"border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300\">1-2周有效性</td>\n                  </tr>\n                  <tr>\n                    <td class=\"border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2 font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100\">覆盖范围</td>\n                    <td class=\"border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300\">广谱异味</td>\n                    <td class=\"border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300\">仅限酸性异味</td>\n                  </tr>\n                  <tr>\n                    <td class=\"border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2 font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100\">天然</td>\n                    <td class=\"border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300\">100%天然碳</td>\n                    <td class=\"border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 px-4 py-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300\">天然矿物化合物</td>\n                  </tr>\n                </tbody>\n              </table>\n            </div>\n\n            <h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50\">\n              最终结论\n            </h2>\n\n            <p class=\"text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200\">\n              虽然两种技术都有其用武之地，但活性炭在猫砂除臭控制方面表现更优。\n              它能够物理捕获广谱异味分子，加上更持久的有效性，\n              使其成为严格除臭的首选。\n            </p>\n\n            <div class=\"bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-900/20 border-l-4 border-green-500 dark:border-green-700 p-6 my-8\">\n              <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-green-800 dark:text-green-200 mb-2\">\n                给猫主人的专业提示\n              </h3>\n              <p class=\"text-green-700 dark:text-green-300\">\n                为了获得最大效果，请选择由椰壳制成的活性炭产品，\n                因为它们提供最高的孔隙率和吸附能力。\n              </p>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          <footer class=\"mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700\">\n            <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 